sentence: may i have a listing of flight numbers from columbus ohio to minneapolis minnesota on monday
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.flight_number, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.state_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.state_name||'"', '"'||v4.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"', '"'||v6.state_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.state_name||'"', '"'||v7.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v8.day_name||'"', v8.year, v8.month_number, v8.day_number,
 '"'||v0.flight_id||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, state v3, airport_service v4, city v5, state v6,
 days v7, date_day v8 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) AND ((v2.city_name = 'COLUMBUS') 
AND ((v2.state_code = ANY v3.state_code) 
AND (v3.state_name = 'OHIO'))))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND ((v5.city_name = 'MINNEAPOLIS') AND ((v5.state_code = ANY v6.state_code) 
AND (v6.state_name = 'MINNESOTA'))))) 
AND ((v0.flight_days = ANY v7.days_code) AND ((v7.day_name = ANY v8.day_name) 
AND (((v8.year =  1993) AND (v8.month_number =  7)) 
AND (v8.day_number =  12))))));

CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE ( CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MINNEAPOLIS ' AND CITY . STATE_CODE IN ( SELECT STATE .
